WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
I welcome you!

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Since people think

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
they are their whole life in search

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
after the big questions about the history of mankind:

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Where are we? Where are we coming from?

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Where are we going to?

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
All religions of the world promise you

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:45.000
the only true answers.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:50.000
But would all just to spend five minutes

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:55.000
to answer simple questions,

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:00.000
there wouldn't be so much suffering by poverty, hunger and war.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:05.000
On the whole world people are drinking coffee.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:10.000
But where the coffee comes from that you just drink?

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:15.000
Is it important to know,

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:20.000
who sold you this coffee?

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:25.000
Do you know the history of coffee?

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:30.000
What had coffee been at first?

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:35.000
How is coffee produced? How did it conquer the world?

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:40.000
I would like to invite you for a coffee

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:45.000
to know the origin of coffee.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:50.000
And then you compare this story

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:55.000
with your religion.

00:01:55.000 --> 00:02:30.000
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coffee

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:35.000
And if you comprehend the fate of the coffee,

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:40.000
and if you have a little common sense,

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:45.000
you will be able

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:50.000
the important questions of mankind

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:55.000
to answer yourself!

